                    </div>
                    <div class="mt-3 p-3 bg-rose-50 rounded-xl border border-rose-200 text-xs text-rose-700">
                        <p class="font-black mb-1">Recommended actions:</p>
                        <p>1. Do not dispense further doses until ADR is investigated</p>
                        <p>2. Inform the prescribing doctor immediately</p>
                        <p>3. Check batch number and lot — report to supplier if batch issue</p>
                        <p>4. Once cleared, click "Clear ADR" in patient's card</p>
